                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-4 border border-white/10">
                            <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Marketing Cookies</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm">Used to deliver relevant advertisements and track campaign effectiveness.</p>
                        </div>
